


Create and run Virtual Enviroment:

# setup venv
python -m venv .venv

# activate vnenv
.venv\Scripts\Activate

# install dependencies
pip install mkdocs-material

# test
mkdocs --version



Setup vscode
Ctrl + Shift + P (Command Palette)
Python: Select Interpreter
Choose `.venv\Scripts\python.exe``




